'''里察·亞克力斯'''（Richard Lambert Thomas Arkless，{{bd|1975年|7月7日}}）是[[蘇格蘭民族黨|蘇格蘭民族黨]]的一位政治人物。他在[[2015年英國大選|2015年英國大選]]中當選[[鄧弗里斯和加洛韋_(英國國會選區)|鄧弗里斯和加洛韋]]選區的英國下議院議員<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.thegazette.co.uk/notice/2334493|title=List of Members returned to Parliament at the General Election 2015 Scotland|work=[[The_Edinburgh_Gazette|The Edinburgh Gazette]]|date=15 May 2015|accessdate=3 June 2015|archive-date=2019-04-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190401063220/https://www.thegazette.co.uk/notice/2334493|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":0">{{Cite web|url = http://dumgal.gov.uk/index.aspx?articleid=14586|title = UK Parliamentary Elections Results 2015 for the Dumfries and Galloway County|date = 2015-05-08|accessdate = 2015-05-09|website = dumgal.gov.uk|publisher = |last = Haswell|first = Alex|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150509122702/http://dumgal.gov.uk/index.aspx?articleid=14586|archivedate = 2015-05-09|deadurl = yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/politics/constituencies/S14000013|title = Election 2015: Dumfries & Galloway Parliamentary constituency|date = |accessdate = 9 May 2015|work = BBC News|publisher = BBC|archive-date = 2015-05-09|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150509124451/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/politics/constituencies/S14000013|dead-url = no}}</ref>。他出生在斯特蘭拉爾，畢業於[[格拉斯哥加里東大學|格拉斯哥加里東大學]]和[[斯克莱德大学|斯克莱德大学]]，在2007年當選蘇格蘭議會議員。

